name: The Weepies Prayer Flags
description:
Authentic and traditional prayer flags but with The Weepies twist on them. Featuring lyrics and album art from Somebody Loved, Gotta Have You, Can't Go Back Now, World Spins Madly On and Be My Thrill.

Custom made with West Wind Flags. For over a thousand years Tibetans have been making and hanging prayer flags. They believe that hanging prayer flags with intention releases positive, energized wishes out to the world on the wind.

Each strand has five flags which are 8x6, 100% cotton and made in Katmandu, Nepal.
